Route Guard Redirect <code>/dashboard/*</code> <code>isAuthenticated</code> <code>/login</code> <code>/screening/*</code> <code>profile_complete AND children.count &gt; 0</code> → профиль или → добавить ребёнка <code>/reports/*</code> <code>isAuthenticated</code> <code>/login</code> <code>/specialist/*</code> <code>role === 'specialist'</code> <code>/dashboard</code> <p>Реализация в <code>ProtectedRoute.tsx</code>: <pre><code>// Текущий guard (только auth):
if (!isAuthenticated) return &lt;Navigate to="/login" /&gt;;

// Нужно добавить:
if (requireProfile &amp;&amp; !profile?.profile_complete) return &lt;Navigate to="/dashboard/profile" /&gt;;
if (requireChild &amp;&amp; childrenCount === 0) return &lt;Navigate to="/dashboard/children/add" /&gt;;
if (requireRole &amp;&amp; profile?.role !== requireRole) return &lt;Navigate to="/dashboard" /&gt;;
</code></pre></p>
